	<key>NSBluetoothAlwaysUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Bluetooth access is needed to discover and connect to the XSC peripheral.</string>
	<key>NSBluetoothPeripheralUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Bluetooth is required to communicate with the XSC device.</string>
	<key>NSBluetoothWhileInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Bluetooth access allows discovery and connection to nearby peripherals while the app is in use.</string>

